<p>Over the course of a few months we spoke to estate agents, and examined the moving process and decided that it would save much more time if users could submit their housing requirements to multiple agents in one hit.</p>

<p><a href="https://propiti.uk" target="_blank">Propiti</a> will be offering agents access to a â€śliving listâ€ť of users who were actively looking to move; thanks to out â€śliving listsâ€ť agents are then able to connect our users to the property they are after in a much more simple and easy way.</p>

<h2 id="so-how-are-we-rolling-this-out">So how are we rolling this out?</h2>
<p>We will be providing our service initially across Hertfordshire, Essex and Cornwall in early 2022. And will begin to roll out across the UK for the rest of 2022 building partnerships in the process.</p>
